  "instructions": [
    "Heat the almond oil in the bottom of a clay or ceramic tagine over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until it is softened and lightly browned.",
    "Add the minced garlic and grated ginger and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the lamb pieces and cook until they are browned on all sides.",
    "Add the almond essence, turmeric, cumin, cayenne pepper, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "Add 2 cups of water to the tagine and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low and simmer, covered, for 2 1/2 hours.",
    "Remove the tagine from the heat and let it cool slightly.",
    "Serve the lamb and sauce over rice or with flatbread."
  ],
